channel.description:
Hi guys/girls I decided I was bored so I decided to make a contest. Starting in 1 hour you will begin working on a project.
Rules- 1. Have to start from scratch 2. Need to post picture of before and after. 3. Must not cheat in any way if you do you will be kicked off of this. 4. You can only place it somewhere that NO ONE ever puts stuff!
Basics- You will begin a project on making a very cool hang out place, it will need to have decorations, cool shops, npc's, etc.. Who ever wins gets PabloScape V3!!
